import React from 'react';
import { BootstrapTable , TableHeaderColumn } from 'react-bootstrap-table';
import Pageadmin from 'layouts/page-admin';
import { Input ,Row , Col , InputGroup , Button } from 'reactstrap';
//import app from 'app';


class listAccessmenu extends React.Component{

render(){
    return(
        <Pageadmin head={'List Access Repository'}>
            <Row>
                <Col md='3'>
                    <InputGroup>
                        <Input type='text'/>
                    </InputGroup>
                </Col>
                <Col md='3'>
                    <InputGroup>
                        <Input type='text'/>
                    </InputGroup>
                </Col>
                <Col md='3'>
                    <InputGroup>
                        <Input type='text'/>
                    </InputGroup>
                </Col>
                <Button type="button" color="default">Cari Data</Button>
            </Row>  
            <BootstrapTable
                      
                        bordered={false}
                        striped
                        pagination={true}
                        >
                          <TableHeaderColumn
                            dataField='DTPERIOD'
                            width='16%'
                            isKey = {true}
                            dataSort>
                            Periode
                          </TableHeaderColumn>
                           <TableHeaderColumn
                            dataField='KATEGORI'
                            width='16%'
                            dataSort>
                            Kategori
                          </TableHeaderColumn>
                          <TableHeaderColumn
                            dataField='COUNTFILE'
                            width='16%'
                            dataSort>
                            Jumlah File
                          </TableHeaderColumn>
                          <TableHeaderColumn
                            dataField="button"
                            dataFormat={this.action.bind(this)}
                            width='16%'
                            dataSort>
                            Action
                          </TableHeaderColumn>
                      </BootstrapTable>
        </Pageadmin>
    )
}

}

export default listAccessmenu;
